snippet.title: Hidden Kittens: Kingdom of Cats - Trailer Steam
snippet.description:
Play now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1726890/Hidden_Kittens_Kingdom_of_Cats/

Get ready for a charming adventure in the Kingdom of Cats! Your mission is to find tons of adorable kittens scattered throughout this magical world. Every corner hides a feline surprise, waiting for you to discover it!
